Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0210.Text: *: I am expecting you have been to Norvik and seen the sleeping people, yes? Their sleeping is the fault of my son.
*: If he had only not been running away with the princess of the faeries...
*: I came here to make an apology in his place, but no, the queen, she will not even listen to me.
*: What is this that you say? My son, he is...dead...?
*: But whatever will I be telling my wife? She will be so very, very sad...
*: Please... (sob) Tell me that this is not true!

Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0410.Text: *: Hellooo! Welcome to the super-secret faerie village!
*: Eek! I'm not supposed to speak to humans! My mummy will be really angry if she finds out!
*: Hellooo! Welcome to the super-secret faerie village!
*: You can't fool us faeries with a simple trick like that! I can seee yooou!

Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0510.Text: *: I'm not allowed to sell things to horrible humans! Go away!
*: You can't fool us faeries with a simple trick like that! I can seee yooou!

Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0610.Text: *: Eeeeeek! Humans! Help me! I don't want to be kidnapped!
*: Eurgh! I hate smelly old dwarfs! Poowee!
*: You can't fool us faeries with a simple trick like that! I can seee yooou!

Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0710.Text: *: What's a human like you doing in a place like this?
*: Just don't go falling in love with any of the faeries, will you? It'll only end in tears.
*: In fact, I'd just turn round and go home if I were you.
*: Hello there, friend! I just love living among the faeries here. It's so relaxing!
*: What are you doing going around looking like that?

Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_House_SUB_0_VOLUME_0.Text: What are you doing in our village? It's supposed to be faeries only!
Get out! You're not allowed here!
You can't fool us faeries with a simple trick like that! I can seee yooou!
What are you doing in our village? It's supposed to be faeries only!
What? Norvik? Oh, that whole thing... I'm sorry to say it, but it's true.
My stupid daughter Aniseed fell in love with a human boy.
She took one of our special faerie treasures<--->the dreamstone<--->and ran off with him and never came back.
He must have tricked her somehow<--->it's the only explanation. Stupid humans!
He probably stole the dreamstone off her, and now she's too ashamed to come home, poor thing...
Ugh, just looking at humans makes me feel sick... Just go away, will you?
You can't fool us faeries with a simple trick like that! I can seee yooou!
What are you doing in our village? It's supposed to be faeries only!
Get out! You're not allowed here!
...Wait!
Is that the dreamstone you've got there?
Wh<--->!? They jumped into the underground lake together and drowned...? Bu<--->
And all because I wouldn't let them be together...?
Here. Take this wakey dust and go back to Norvik.
You can use it to lift the curse I put on the place. It's what Aniseed would have wanted...
Oh, Annie... My little girl... What have I done...?
You can't fool us faeries with a simple trick like that! I can seee yooou!
{LEADER} obtains some wakey dust!

Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_House_SUB_0_ACTOR_01.Text: ...Thank you. I'm... I'm grateful for your help.
But don't think that this means I like humans now. I don't. Now go away. Just...go.
You can't fool us faeries with a simple trick like that! I can seee yooou!
...Thank you. I'm... I'm grateful for your help.
But I have to follow the faerie rules.
And the faerie rules say that you have to leave. If you don't, there'll only be another tragedy...
You can't fool us faeries with a simple trick like that! I can seee yooou!

Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_Out_SUB_0_ACTOR_0910.Text: *: You know, I see monsters in the village from time to time. Usually, I just chase them off, but there was one that refused to budge one evening recently. Awfully strange stuff.
*: Come to think of it, I'd just finished getting dinner ready, so maybe it was drawn by the scent of my inspired cooking...

Txt_Talk_ElfVillage_Out_SUB_0_VOLUME_083.Text: {LEADER} calms the monster with a soothing voice and tells it about Monty's monster menagerie...
